---
title: Cherry-Glazed Beef Rump with Roast Veggie Chunks & Sautéed Cabbage
description: Round out the warmer months with this spectacular steak, drizzled with a sticky-sweet cherry glaze. And for the real 'cherry' on top, we’ve added roasted veggies and glowing sauteed cabbage depth of flavour to boot!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/64a20af291cac2bc8b80877a-2411fdd5.jpeg
